.DT
title
$MUDNAME$ player help
title

.SH Name
.SI 5
title - sets the player title
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
title
title <title>
title none
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This command sets your player title.  The player title is the bit that will
show up before your name, as in Mr Turrican.

The 'none' argument sets the title back to nothing.

You can use the 'brief' command to turn off titles from being displayed
by people.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> title
> title mr
> title none
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
brief
.EP
